ActAppropriation Act No. 1, 2010-11
PrecisAppointment of CHRISTOPHER COOTER as High Commissioner for Canada to the Federal Republic of Nigeria and Permanent Observer of Canada to the Economic Community of West African States (ECOWAS); and DAVID COLLINS as High Commissioner for Canada to the Republic of Kenya with concurrent accreditation to the Republic of Uganda and as Permanent Representative of Canada to the United Nations Centre for Human Settlements and to the United Nations Environment Programme, in Nairobi.
